Newest Filings











CMC Capital Partners II, L.P.  Financing
CMC Capital Partners II, L.P. just submitted form D announcing  Indefinite equity financing.  CMC Capital Partners II, L.P. was able to sell $182,000,000. The total private offering amount was Indefinite. The financing was made by 7 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $0. The financing document was filed on 2017-05-30. CMC Capital Partners II, L.P. is based in  C/O PO BOX 309 UGLAND HOUSE GRAND CAYMAN KY1-1104. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The firm's revenue range is Decline to Disclose. The form was signed by  Ruigang Li.





